Package: chipAnalyseR
Type: Package
Title: R package for rapid ChIP-seq data analysis and visualisation. Especially bigWig files and BED files
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Claudia Robens
Maintainer: claudia-robens@web.de
Description: Useful package to anylyse and visualise ChIP-seq data. Output file formats like bigWig files and BED files and be read in an efficient way thanks to bwtool. The package is a combination of R code with elements written in C. 
License: MIT
LazyData: TRUE
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
Depends: data.table, ggplot2, cowplot, parallel
